Special guest Jasmine Chiswell joins me! Rose McGowan is a victim. Does that giver her the right to victimize others? NeNe Leakes' husband is seeing other women! And she's seeing other men! Why are they still married? And more of today's hottest headlines, including Tom Hanks, Harvey Weinstein, Disneyland, Kesha, Broadway, Liam Hemsworth, Las Vegas, Kate Becksinale, the NBA, Ben Affleck, The View and MORE! Watch!
